author: GameSpot
description:
Rainbow Six Siege has survived ten of the most tumultuous years video games have ever seen. Not only that, but it's flourished in a space that is always trying to capitalize on the "next big thing." On the back of the game's 10th anniversary, GameSpot flew to Canada to speak to the team at Ubisoft Montreal about the tactical shooter that stuck to its guns and defied an industry.

#rainbowsix #rainbow6 #rainbowsixsiege
title: How Rainbow Six Siege Defied An Industry

author: GameSpot
description:
Massive Entertainment expands its take of Pandora with a new story that transforms the world and adds some cool new elements to an already solid game.

When it was released in 2023, Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora succeeded in the daunting task of bringing its own kind of life to the world of James Cameron's Avatar movies. Developer Massive Entertainment wisely chose not to retell the story of the films, instead weaving a tale on the other side of the moon of Pandora where the films take place.

#avatar #avatarfrontiersofpandora #avatarfromtheashes
title: Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora – From the Ashes Hands-On Impressions
